* NEW: Added Lyrics searching. Now when viewing the info page for a track you can click a link and search Leo's Lyrics
* NEW: Added some sample theme images to the installer so you can get an idea of what to expect...
* NEW: Jinzora will now write ID3v2 tags as well as ID3v1...
* CHG: Changed the way getID3 reads file data, am now using the more aggressive scan method to ensure results everytime
* CHG: Now a filename.txt file (track description) will over-ride the ID3 comment field on display
* CHG: Added better support for media that is found out of place...
