Jinzora 0.3 (8.22.03)

* Fixed some minor bugs with the iPod - ephPod sync (directory size was reporting incorrectly)
* Added a fully functional upload center - gives users the ability to upload a single ZIP file containting all the music they'd like to add. The user chooses a Genre, specifies the Artist and Album and if they do not exists they are created on the fly. Then if they user uploaded a ZIP file it is extracted into the new directory structure. NOTE: Make sure the PHP upload limit is set high enough for the files that you'll be uploading and that the user that the webserver is running as has permissions to the filesystem

Jinzora 0.3pre2 (8.21.03)

* Added iPod/ephPod sync system - allows users to select which artists to sync to their iPod using ephPod

