Jinzora 0.2 (8.18.03)

* First release of Jinzora after ground up rewrite. New features are:
* Drop down lists for Genre, Artist, Album in the header
* Ability to download albums or single songs as a single zip file (to make it easier)
* Ability to play entire Genre, Artist, Album with a single click

